{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-002", "source_id": "song-shangsong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·002.1", "text_original": "猗嗟嗟烈祖，有秩斯祜。申錫無疆，及爾斯所。既載清酤，賚我思成。", "text_normalized": "猗嗟嗟烈祖，有秩斯祜。申錫無疆，及爾斯所。既載清酤，賚我思成。", "notes": "烈祖 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-002", "source_id": "song-shangsong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·002.2", "text_original": "亦有和羹，既戒既平。鬷假無言，時靡有爭。綏我眉壽，黃耇無疆。", "text_normalized": "亦有和羹，既戒既平。鬷假無言，時靡有爭。綏我眉壽，黃耇無疆。", "notes": "烈祖 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-002", "source_id": "song-shangsong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·002.3", "text_original": "約軝錯衡，八鸞鶬鶬。以假以享，我受命溥將。自天降康，豐年穰穰。", "text_normalized": "約軝錯衡，八鸞鶬鶬。以假以享，我受命溥將。自天降康，豐年穰穰。", "notes": "烈祖 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-002", "source_id": "song-shangsong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·002.4", "text_original": "來假來饗，降福無疆。顧予烝嘗，湯孫之將。", "text_normalized": "來假來饗，降福無疆。顧予烝嘗，湯孫之將。", "notes": "烈祖 Chinese stanza 4."}
